channel.title: ______ Is already online
channel.description:

________ is already online! ________ is already online! ________ is already online! ________ is already online! ________ is already online!
Becuase everyone is trying to get on, so its not just my account thats logged on. Any suggestions? Auto restarter, fix the problem?
